{"tid":1156638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗起幾十年後冇乜人再講廣東話，好心酸","createTime":"2019-05-15T17:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T17:32:43.000Z","uid":238361,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf37c03ff904228e26bba7892c3920633091e6df","tid":1156638,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T17:32:43.000Z","msg":"考試連廣東話都唔使識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新幾代逐漸講蝗語 (普通話) 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出街以後剩係會聽到些些 些些<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明係自己嘅地方，用自己家鄉語言先親切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變曬蝗語好似唔係自己屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊嗰啲都唔係自己人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時我喺度諗，如果當啲大陸呢講蝗語嗰陣，全香港嘅真香港人都扮聽唔明、唔理鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地用蝗語嗌救命都唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地係咪就知死，要學廣東話？但依家根本就逆其道而行，本身嘅真香港人都學普通話、講得愈黎愈多普通話，咪俾人同化囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明真香港人仲多過腥港人架，點解要俾人文化入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果大家同心合力扮聽唔明蝗語、排鳩佢地，我覺得廣東話仲保留到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我地會被逼講少咗廣東話，而唔係逼佢地喺度生活就要講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}